  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing puzzle game where you combine neighboring cards to form poker hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your arrow keys to move the cards. When two cards touch, they merge into one!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 50 Levels that will challenge you to form different poker hands;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Designed for experienced poker players and newcomers alike (you do not need to know how to play poker to enjoy this game!);</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Original soundtrack, composed specially for this game.</p></li></ul>",
